The paper could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category as it deals with entity linking and context, which are important topics in CL. 

The paper may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a model for entity relatedness that uses entity aware word embeddings, which is a common technique in machine learning. 

The paper could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as it deals with entity relatedness, which is an important task in AI.
